<plot>Following the explosive finale of series four of Lost, this special attempts to find out the answers to the questions on every viewer's mind from the creators themselves- executive producers and writers Carlton Cuse and Damon Lindelof, as well as director Jack Bender and actors Michael Emerson and Alan Dale. We also find out which questions some of Lost's celebrity fans are dying to have answered.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?343922</url></doc>
